### StepWizard::Footer

The Footer component renders the navigation area of the wizard and displays the user’s progress.

The footer layout includes:

* Back button (optional, hidden on the first step)
* Progress bar (optional)
* Cancel button (optional)
* Continue button (shown when the current step is not the last one)
* Submit button (shown on the final step)

